plot: Target in hand, the Mandalorian must now contend with scavengers.

After fighting off some bounty hunters who were tracking the child, the Mandalorian returns to his ship to find it scavenged by Jawas. Kuill directs him to trade with the Jawas in order to get the parts back. The Jawas demand he retrieve "The Egg." When the Mandalorian enters the cave, he discovers that it is the nest of a giant horned beast that attacks him.
